    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-size: 9pt; font-style: italic;}\n.html-preview .a5 {className: a5; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Т<span class=\"leading\"></span>А Қ И Қ </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">(гаров шартномаси бўйича)</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#2}Нотариал округ номи</span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Тақиқнома тасдиқланган сана</span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#4}Гаров шартномаси бўйича таъқиқ киритаётган нотариал идора манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">даги</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи нотариус </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> Ўзбекистон Республикаси «Нотариат тўғрисида»ги Қонунининг 64-моддасига асосан, </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#7}Шартнома қайд этилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Шартнома қайд қилинган реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> реестр рақами билан қайд қилинган (ипотека) шартномаси бўйича гаровга қўйилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Гаровга қўйилган автотранспорт эгасининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#13}Гаровга қўйилган автотранспорт эгасининг рўйхатдан ўтган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уйда яшовчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}Гаровга қўйилган автотранспорт эгасининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">га </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Автотранспорт гувоҳномаси қайд этган ҳудуд</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Автотранспорт гувоҳномаси қайд этилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да берилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Автотранспорт гувоҳномасига берилган серия рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-серия рақамли транспорт воситасини қайд этиш гувоҳномасига асосан тегишли бўлган, </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Автотранспорт русуми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> русумли, </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Автотранспорт воситасининг ишлаб чиқилган йили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда ишлаб чиқарилган, двигатель рақами </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Автотранспорт воситасининг двигатель рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span>кузов рақами </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Автотранспорт воситасининг кузов рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span>шасси рақами – </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Автотранспорт воситасининг шасси рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span>ранги – </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#23}Автотранспорт воситасининг ранги</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span>давлат рақами белгиси </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#24}Давлат рақам белгиси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> бўлган автотранспорт воситасини кредит шартномасидаги мажбуриятлар тўлиқ бажарилмагунга қадар бошқа шахсга ўтказилишини тақиқлайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариус <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n</div></div>",
